handist.collections.dist

Class MapEntryDispatcher<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • handist.collections.dist.MapEntryDispatcher<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - : The key type of map entry
    V - : The value type of map entry
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.esotericsoftware.kryo.KryoSerializable, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MultiMapEntryDispatcher

    public class MapEntryDispatcher<K,V>
extends Object
implements com.esotericsoftware.kryo.KryoSerializable, Serializable
    DistMap has this class in order to dispatch entris to places defined by Distribution. Relocate entries between places by calling MapEntryDispatcher.TeamOperations.dispatch(). Dhe dispatched entries are added to original DistMap. Please be careful that reference relationships like multiple references to one object are not maintained.
    Author:
    yoshikikawanishi
